ont_ball_5\n- [8-9] back_ball_1, back_ball_2\n- [10] pool_amount\n- [11] sales_amount\n- [12] created_at\n- [13] updated_at\n\n我的预测脚本里写的是 `record[2:7]` 但实际上应该是 `record[3:8]`！让我修复这个问题。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"原来是索引偏移问题！修复预测脚本：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"callfunctionkv06ue784t4w1","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"def analyze_front_balls(records):\n    \"\"\"分析前区号码（红球 1-35）频率\"\"\"\n    front_balls = []\n    for record in records:\n        # 前区是 record[3:8] (front_ball_1 到 front_ball_5)\n        front_balls.extend(record[3:8])\n    return Counter(front_balls)","oldText":"def analyze_front_balls(records):\n    \"\"\"分析前区号码（红球 1-35）频率\"\"\"\n    front_balls = []\n    for record in records:\n        # 前区是 record[2:7] (去掉日期后的5个号码)\n        front_balls.extend(record[2:7])\n    return Counter(front_balls)"},{"newText":"def analyze_back_balls(records):\n    \"\"\"分析后区号码（蓝球 1-12）频率\"\"\"\n    back_balls = []\n    for record in records:\n        # 后区是 record[8:10]\n        back_balls.extend(record[8:10])\n    return Counter(back_balls)","oldText":"def analyze_back_balls(records):\n    \"\"\"分析后区号码（蓝球 1-12）频率\"\"\"\n    back_balls = []\n    for record in records:\n        # 后区是 record[7:9]\n        back_balls.extend(record[7:9])\n    return Counter(back_balls)"}],"path":"/workspace/projects/workspace/skills/super-lotto/scripts/predict.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":475,"output":667,"cacheRead":54203,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":55345,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778129258573,"responseId":"064b4c6abf51ae55cc7b8eb9d99cb268"},{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"callfunctionkv06ue784t4w1","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced 2 block(s) in /workspace/projects/workspace/skills/super-lotto/scripts/predict.py."}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1778129266909},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在还需要修复 calculate_missing_days 函数里的列名问题。让我也检查一下那个函数的 SQL 查询是否正确。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"callfunctionr2rga94enapc1","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"    cursor.execute(f'''\n            SELECT issue_number FROM lottery_records \n            WHERE front_ball_1={ball} OR front_ball_2={ball} OR front_ball_3={ball} OR front_ball_4={ball} OR front_ball_5={ball}\n            ORDER BY issue_number DESC\n            LIMIT 1\n        ''')","oldText":"    cursor.execute(f'''\n            SELECT issue_number FROM lottery_records \n            WHERE {columns} LIKE '%{ball}%'\n            ORDER BY issue_number DESC\n            LIMIT 1\n        ''')"},{"newText":"    cursor.execute(f'''\n            SELECT issue_number FROM lottery_records \n            WHERE back_ball_1={ball} OR back_ball_2={ball}\n            ORDER BY issue_number DESC\n            LIMIT 1\n        ''')","oldText":"    cursor.execute(f'''\n            SELECT issue_number FROM lottery_records \n            WHERE {columns} LIKE '%{ball}%'\n            ORDER BY issue_number DESC\n            LIMIT 1\n        ''')"}],"path":"/workspace/projects/workspace/skills/super-lotto/scripts/predict.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":159,"output":336,"cacheRead":55099,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":55594,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778129266910,"responseId":"064b4c730517f4f7f6be6940c3717c77"},{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"callfunctionr2rga94enapc1","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"status\": \"error\",\n  \"tool\": \"edit\",\n  \"error\": \"edits[0] and edits[1] overlap in /workspace/projects/workspace/skills/super-lotto/scripts/predict.py. Merge them into one edit or target disjoint regions.\"\n}"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1778129271972},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"两个编辑重叠了。让我重新读取文件然后一起修复。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"callfunction9j4s4jqtl05h1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/workspace/projects/workspace/skills/super-lotto/scripts/predict.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":94,"output":69,"cacheRead":55547,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":55710,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778129271973,"responseId":"064b4c78518817b889e3a93c56b33920"},{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"callfunction9j4s4jqtl05h1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\n大乐透预测模型\n基于历史数据频率分析和遗漏值统计生成推荐号码\n\"\"\"\n\nimport sqlite3\nimport random\nfrom collections import Counter\nfrom datetime import datetime\nimport argparse\n\nDB_PATH = 'data/super_lotto.db'\n\ndef get_connection():\n    \"\"\"获取数据库连接\"\"\"\n    return sqlite3.connect(DB_PATH)\n\ndef get_all_records(limit=None):\n    \"\"\"获取所有开奖记录\"\"\"\n    conn = get_connection()\n    cursor = conn.cursor()\n    if limit:\n        cursor.execute(f'''\n            SELECT * FROM lottery_records \n            ORDER BY issue_number DESC \n            LIMIT {limit}\n        ''')\n    else:\n        cursor.execute('SELECT * FROM lottery_records ORDER BY issue_number DESC')\n    records = cursor.fetchall()\n    conn.close()\n    return records\n\ndef analyze_front_balls(records):\n    \"\"\"分析前区号码（红球 1-35）频率\"\"\"\n    front_balls = []\n    for record in records:\n        # 前区是 record[3:8] (front_ball_1 到 front_ball_5)\n        front_balls.extend(record[3:8])\n    return Counter(front_balls)\n\ndef analyze_back_balls(records):\n    \"\"\"分析后区号码（蓝球 1-12）频率\"\"\"\n    back_balls = []\n    for record in records:\n        # 后区是 record[8:10]\n        back_balls.extend(record[8:10])\n    return Counter(back_balls)\n\ndef calculate_missing_days(records, ball_type='front'):\n    \"\"\"计算号码遗漏天数（距上次出现的期数）\"\"\"\n    conn = get_connection()\n    cursor = conn.cursor()\n    \n    if ball_type == 'front':\n        max_ball = 35\n        columns = 'front_ball_1, front_ball_2, front_ball_3, front_ball_4, front_ball_5'\n    else:\n        max_ball = 12\n        columns = 'back_ball_1, back_ball_2'\n    \n    cursor.execute(f'''\n        SELECT issue_number FROM lottery_records \n        ORDER BY issue_number DESC\n    ''')\n    issues = [row[0] for row in cursor.fetchall()]\n    latest_issue = issues[0] if issues else 0\n    \n    missing_days = {}\n    for ball in range(1, max_ball + 1):\n        cursor.execute(f'''\n            SELECT issue_number FROM lottery_records \n            WHERE {columns} LIKE '%{ball}%'\n            ORDER BY issue_number DESC\n            LIMIT 1\n        ''')\n        result = cursor.fetchone()\n        if result:\n            missing_days[ball] = latest_issue - result[0]\n        else:\n            missing_days[ball] = latest_issue  # 从未出现\n    \n    conn.close()\n    return missing_days\n\ndef generate_hot_number_prediction(records, count=5):\n    \"\"\"基于热号生成预测（前区）\"\"\"\n    front_freq = analyze_front_balls(records)\n    # 选择出现频率最高的号码\n    hot_balls = front_freq.most_common(count)\n    return [ball for ball, freq in hot_balls]\n\ndef generate_cold_number_prediction(records, count=5):\n    \"\"\"基于冷号生成预测（前区）\"\"\"\n    front_freq = analyze_front_balls(records)\n    # 找出所有号码\n    all_balls = set(range(1, 36))\n    appeared = set(front_freq.keys())\n    never_appeared = all_balls - appeared\n    \n    # 选择出现次数最少的号码\n    if len(front_freq) >= count:\n        cold_balls = [ball for ball, freq in front_freq.most_common()[-count:]]\n    else:\n        cold_balls = []\n    \n    # 如果不够5个，补充从未出现的号码\n    result = cold_balls + list(never_appeared)\n    return result[:count]\n\ndef generate_missing_prediction(records, count=5):\n    \"\"\"基于遗漏值生成预测（前区）\"\"\"\n    missing = calculate_missing_days(records, 'front')\n    # 选择遗漏值最大的号码\n    sorted_missing = sorted(missing.items(), key=lambda x: x[1], reverse=True)\n    return [ball for ball, days in sorted_missing[:count]]\n\ndef generate_random_prediction(count=5, ball_range=(1, 35)):\n    \"\"\"生成随机号码\"\"\"\n    return sorted(random.sample(range(ball_range[0], ball_range[1] + 1), count))\n\ndef generate_balanced_prediction(records):\n    \"\"\"生成均衡型预测（结合热号、冷号、随机）\"\"\"\n    # 2个热号\n    hot = generate_hot_number_prediction(records, 2)\n    # 1个冷号\n    cold = generate_cold_number_prediction(records, 1)\n    # 2个遗漏值大的号\n    missing = generate_missing_prediction(records, 2)\n    \n    # 合并并去重\n    combined = hot + cold + missing\n    seen = set()\n    result = []\n    for ball in combined:\n        if ball not in seen and len(result) < 5:\n            seen.add(ball)\n            result.append(ball)\n    \n    # 如果不够5个，随机补足\n    while len(result) < 5:\n        ball = random.randint(1, 35)\n        if ball not in seen:\n            seen.add(ball)\n            result.append(ball)\n    \n    return sorted(result)\n\ndef generate_ml_style_prediction(records):\n    \"\"\"基于加权评分的预测（模拟简单ML模型）\"\"\"\n    front_freq = analyze_front_balls(records)\n    missing = calculate_missing_days(records, 'front')\n    \n    # 计算每个号码的加权分数\n    max_freq = max(front_freq.values()) if front_freq else 1\n    max_missing = max(missing.values()) if missing else 1\n    \n    scores = {}\n    for ball in range(1, 36):\n        freq_score = front_freq.get(ball, 0) / max_freq  # 频率分数\n        missing_score = missing.get(ball, 0) / max_missing  # 遗漏分数\n        # 加权：频率占40%，遗漏占60%\n        scores[ball] = freq_score * 0.4 + missing_score * 0.6\n    \n    # 选择分数最高的5个号码\n    sorted_balls = sorted(scores.items(), key=lambda x: x[1], reverse=True)\n    return [ball for ball, score in sorted_balls[:5]]\n\ndef print_prediction(title, front_balls, back_balls):\n    \"\"\"打印预测结果\"\"\"\n    print(f\"\\n{'='*50}\")\n    print(f\"📊 {title}\")\n    print(f\"{'='*50}\")\n    print(f\"🎱 前区号码: {' '.join(f'{b:02d}' for b in front_balls)}\")\n    print(f\"🔵 后区号码: {' '.join(f'{b:02d}' for b in back_balls)}\")\n    print(f\"{'='*50}\")\n\ndef main():\n    parser = argparse.ArgumentParser(description='大乐透预测模型')\n    parser.add_argument('--strategy', '-s', type=str, \n                       choices=['hot', 'cold', 'missing', 'balanced', 'ml', 'all'],\n                       default='all', help='预测策略')\n    parser.add_argument('--count', '-c', type=int, default=3, help='生成几组号码')\n    parser.add_argument('--history', type=int, default=None, help='使用最近多少期数据')\n    args = parser.parse_args()\n    \n    records = get_all_records(args.history)\n    \n    if not records:\n        print(\"❌ 数据库中没有数据，请先运行 fetch_history.py 抓取数据\")\n        return\n    \n    print(f\"\\n🎲 大乐透预测模型\")\n    print(f\"📈 数据来源: 最近 {len(records)} 期历史数据\")\n    \n    # 生成后区号码（固定策略）\n    back_balls_pool = list(range(1, 13))\n    \n    if args.strategy == 'all':\n        # 生成多种策略的预测\n        strategies = [\n            ('🔥 热号策略 (高频号码)', 'hot'),\n            ('❄️ 冷号策略 (低频号码)', 'cold'),\n            ('📈 遗漏策略 (长未出现)', 'missing'),\n            ('⚖️ 均衡策略 (冷热混合)', 'balanced'),\n            ('🤖 ML加权策略 (频率+遗漏)', 'ml'),\n        ]\n        \n        for name, strategy in strategies:\n            for i in range(args.count):\n                if strategy == 'hot':\n                    front = generate_hot_number_prediction(records, 5)\n                elif strategy == 'cold':\n                    front = generate_cold_number_prediction(records, 5)\n                elif strategy == 'missing':\n                    front = generate_missing_prediction(records, 5)\n                elif strategy == 'balanced':\n                    front = generate_balanced_prediction(records)\n                else:\n                    front = generate_ml_style_prediction(records)\n                \n                back = sorted(random.sample(back_balls_pool, 2))\n                title = f\"{name} 第{i+1}组\"\n                print_prediction(title, front, back)\n    else:\n        # 生成指定策略的预测\n        for i in range(args.count):\n            if args.strategy == 'hot':\n                front = generate_hot_number_prediction(records, 5)\n            elif args.strategy == 'cold':\n                front = generate_cold_number_prediction(records, 5)\n            elif args.strategy == 'missing':\n                front = generate_missing_prediction(records, 5)\n            elif args.strategy == 'balanced':\n                front = generate_balanced_prediction(records)\n            else:\n                front = generate_ml_style_prediction(records)\n            \n            back = sorted(random.sample(back_balls_pool, 2))\n            title = f\"预测 第{i+1}组\"\n            print_prediction(title, front, back)\n    \n    # 打印统计信息\n    print(f\"\\n📊 历史数据统计 (前区)\")\n    front_freq = analyze_front_balls(records)\n    print(f\"   最热号码: {front_freq.most_common(3)}\")\n    print(f\"   最冷号码: {front_freq.most_common()[-3:]}\")\n\nif __name__ == '__main__':\n    main()\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1778129274094},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我需要修复 calculate_missing_days 函数中的 SQL 查询，使用明确的列名而不是 LIKE。让我重新写这个函数。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"callfunction5uoxxtmszbuo1","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"def calculate_missing_days(records, ball_type='front'):\n    \"\"\"计算号码遗漏天数（距上次出现的期数）\"\"\"\n    conn = get_connection()\n    cursor = conn.cursor()\n    \n    max_ball = 35 if ball_type == 'front' else 12\n    \n    cursor.execute('''\n        SELECT issue_number FROM lottery_records \n        ORDER BY issue_number DESC\n    ''')\n    issues = [row[0] for row in cursor.fetchall()]\n    latest_issue = int(issues[0]) if issues else 0\n    \n    missing_days = {}\n    for ball in range(1, max_ball + 1):\n        if ball_type == 'front':\n            cursor.execute('''\n                SELECT issue_number FROM lottery_records \n                WHERE front_ball_1=? OR front_ball_2=? OR front_ball_3=? OR front_ball_4=? OR front_ball_5=?\n                ORDER BY issue_number DESC\n                LIMIT 1\n            ''', (ball, ball, ball, ball, ball))\n        else:\n            cursor.execute('''\n                SELECT issue_number FROM lottery_records \n                WHERE back_ball_1=? OR back_ball_2=?\n                ORDER BY issue_number DESC\n                LIMIT 1\n            ''', (ball, ball))\n        \n        result = cursor.fetchone()\n        if result:\n            missing_days[ball] = latest_issue - int(result[0])\n        else:\n            missing_days[ball] = latest_issue  # 从未出现\n    \n    conn.close()\n    return missing_days","oldText":"def calculate_missing_days(records, ball_type='front'):\n    \"\"\"计算号码遗漏天数（距上次出现的期数）\"\"\"\n    conn = get_connection()\n    cursor = conn.cursor()\n    \n    if ball_type == 'front':\n        max_ball = 35\n        columns = 'front_ball_1, front_ball_2, front_ball_3, front_ball_4, front_ball_5'\n    else:\n        max_ball = 12\n        columns = 'back_ball_1, back_ball_2'\n    \n    cursor.execute('''\n        SELECT issue_number FROM lottery_records \n        ORDER BY issue_number DESC\n    ''')\n    issues = [row[0] for row in cursor.fetchall()]\n    latest_issue = issues[0] if issues else 0\n    \n    missing_days = {}\n    for ball in range(1, max_ball + 1):\n        cursor.execute(f'''\n            SELECT issue_number FROM lottery_records \n            WHERE {columns} LIKE '%{ball}%'\n            ORDER BY issue_number DESC\n            LIMIT 1\n        ''')\n        result = cursor.fetchone()\n        if result:\n            missing_days[ball] = latest_issue - result[0]\n        else:\n            missing_days[ball] = latest_issue  # 从未出现\n    \n    conn.close()\n    return missing_days"}],"path":"/workspace/projects/workspace/skills/super-lotto/scripts/predict.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":10852,"output":819,"cacheRead":47035,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":58706,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778129274095,"responseId":"064b4c7a562a0ebafb8efdc50eed7dbb"},{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"callfunction5uoxxtmszbuo1","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"status\": \"error\",\n  \"tool\": \"edit\",\n  \"error\": \"Could not find the exact text in /workspace/projects/workspace/skills/super-lotto/scripts/predict.py. The old text must match exactly including all whitespace and newlines.\\nCurrent file contents:\\n#!/usr/bin/env python3\\n\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n大乐透预测模型\\n基于历史数据频率分析和遗漏值统计生成推荐号码\\n\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n\\nimport sqlite3\\nimport random\\nfrom collections import Counter\\nfrom datetime import datetime\\nimport argparse\\n\\nDB_PATH = 'data/super_lotto.db'\\n\\ndef get_connection():\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"获取数据库连接\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    return sqlite3.connect(DB_PATH)\\n\\ndef get_all_records(limit=None):\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"获取所有开奖记录\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    conn = get_connection()\\n    cursor = conn.cursor()\\n    if limit:\\n        cursor.execute(f'''\\n            SELECT * FROM lottery_records \\n            ORDER BY issue_number DESC \\n            LIMIT {limit}\\n        ''')\\n    else:\\n        cursor.execute('SELECT * FROM lottery_records ORDER BY issue_number DESC')\\n    records = cursor.fetchall()\\n    conn.close()\\n    return records\\n\\ndef analyze_front_balls(records):\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"分析前区号码（红球 1-35）频率\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    front_balls = []\\n   \\n... (truncated)\"\n}"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1778129286090},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"编辑失败了，让我直接重写整个文件。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"callfunctionqhj7us47sl4m1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\n大乐透预测模型\n基于历史数据频率分析和遗漏值统计生成推荐号码\n\"\"\"\n\nimport sqlite3\nimport random\nfrom collections import Counter\nfrom datetime import datetime\nimport argparse\n\nDB_PATH = 'data/super_lotto.db'\n\ndef get_connection():\n    \"\"\"获取数据库连接\"\"\"\n    return sqlite3.connect(DB_PATH)\n\ndef get_all_records(limit=None):\n    \"\"\"获取所有开奖记录\"\"\"\n    conn = get_connection()\n    cursor = conn.cursor()\n    if limit:\n        cursor.execute(f'''\n            SELECT * FROM lottery_records \n            ORDER BY issue_number DESC \n            LIMIT {limit}\n        ''')\n    else:\n        cursor.execute('SELECT * FROM lottery_records ORDER BY issue_number DESC')\n    records = cursor.fetchall()\n    conn.close()\n    return records\n\ndef analyze_front_balls(records):\n    \"\"\"分析前区号码（红球 1-35）频率\"\"\"\n    front_balls = []\n    for record in records:\n        # 前区是 record[3:8] (front_ball_1 到 front_ball_5)\n        front_balls.extend(record[3:8])\n    return Counter(front_balls)\n\ndef analyze_back_balls(records):\n    \"\"\"分析后区号码（蓝球 1-12）频率\"\"\"\n    back_balls = []\n    for record in records:\n        # 后区是 record[8:10]\n        back_balls.extend(record[8:10])\n    return Counter(back_balls)\n\ndef calculate_missing_days(records, ball_type='front'):\n    \"\"\"计算号码遗漏天数（距上次出现的期数）\"\"\"\n    conn = get_connection()\n    cursor = conn.cursor()\n    \n    max_ball = 35 if ball_type == 'front' else 12\n    \n    cursor.execute('''\n        SELECT issue_number FROM lottery_records \n        ORDER BY issue_number DESC\n    ''')\n    issues = [row[0] for row in cursor.fetchall()]\n    latest_issue = int(issues[0]) if issues else 0\n    \n    missing_days = {}\n    for ball in range(1, max_ball + 1):\n        if ball_type == 'front':\n            cursor.execute('''\n                SELECT issue_number FROM lottery_records \n                WHERE front_ball_1=? OR front_ball_2=? OR front_ball_3=? OR front_ball_4=? OR front_ball_5=?\n                ORDER BY issue_number DESC\n                LIMIT 1\n            ''', (ball, ball, ball, ball, ball))\n        else:\n            cursor.execute('''\n                SELECT issue_number FROM lottery_records \n                WHERE back_ball_1=? OR back_ball_2=?\n                ORDER BY issue_number DESC\n                LIMIT 1\n            ''', (ball, ball))\n        \n        result = cursor.fetchone()\n        if result:\n            missing_days[ball] = latest_issue - int(result[0])\n        else:\n            missing_days[ball] = latest_issue  # 从未出现\n    \n    conn.close()\n    return missing_days\n\ndef generate_hot_number_prediction(records, count=5):\n    \"\"\"基于热号生成预测（前区）\"\"\"\n    front_freq = analyze_front_balls(records)\n    # 选择出现频率最高的号码\n    hot_balls = front_freq.most_common(count)\n    return [ball for ball, freq in hot_balls]\n\ndef generate_cold_number_prediction(records, count=5):\n    \"\"\"基于冷号生成预测（前区）\"\"\"\n    front_freq = analyze_front_balls(records)\n    # 找出所有号码\n    all_balls = set(range(1, 36))\n    appeared = set(front_freq.keys())\n    never_appeared = all_balls - appeared\n    \n    # 选择出现次数最少的号码\n    if len(front_freq) >= count:\n        cold_balls = [ball for ball, freq in front_freq.most_common()[-count:]]\n    else:\n        cold_balls = []\n    \n    # 如果不够5个，补充从未出现的号码\n    result = cold_balls + list(never_appeared)\n    return result[:count]\n\ndef generate_missing_prediction(records, count=5):\n    \"\"\"基于遗漏值生成预测（前区）\"\"\"\n    missing = calculate_missing_days(records, 'front')\n    # 选择遗漏值最大的号码\n    sorted_missing = sorted(missing.items(), key=lambda x: x[1], reverse=True)\n    return [ball for ball, days in sorted_missing[:count]]\n\ndef generate_random_prediction(count=5, ball_range=(1, 35)):\n    \"\"\"生成随机号码\"\"\"\n    return sorted(random.sample(range(ball_range[0], ball_range[1] + 1), count))\n\ndef generate_balanced_prediction(records):\n    \"\"\"生成均衡型预测（结合热号、冷号、随机）\"\"\"\n    # 2个热号\n    hot = generate_hot_number_prediction(records, 2)\n    # 1个冷号\n    cold = generate_cold_number_prediction(records, 1)\n    # 2个遗漏值大的号\n    missing = generate_missing_prediction(records, 2)\n    \n    # 合并并去重\n    combined = hot + cold + missing\n    seen = set()\n    result = []\n    for ball in combined:\n        if ball not in seen and len(result) < 5:\n            seen.add(ball)\n            result.append(ball)\n    \n    # 如果不够5个，随机补足\n    while len(result) < 5:\n        ball = random.randint(1, 35)\n        if ball not in seen:\n            seen.add(ball)\n            result.append(ball)\n    \n    return sorted(result)\n\ndef generate_ml_style_prediction(records):\n    \"\"\"基于加权评分的预测（模拟简单ML模型）\"\"\"\n    front_freq = analyze_front_balls(records)\n    missing = calculate_missing_days(records, 'front')\n    \n    # 计算每个号码的加权分数\n    max_freq = max(front_freq.values()) if front_freq else 1\n    max_missing = max(missing.values()) if missing else 1\n    \n    scores = {}\n    for ball in range(1, 36):\n        freq_score = front_freq.get(ball, 0) / max_freq  # 频率分数\n        missing_score = missing.get(ball, 0) / max_missing  # 遗漏分数\n        # 加权：频率占40%，遗漏占60%\n        scores[ball] = freq_score * 0.4 + missing_score * 0.6\n    \n    # 选择分数最高的5个号码\n    sorted_balls = sorted(scores.items(), key=lambda x: x[1], reverse=True)\n    return [ball for ball, score in sorted_balls[:5]]\n\ndef generate_back_balls_prediction(records, count=2):\n    \"\"\"生成后区号码预测\"\"\"\n    back_freq = analyze_back_balls(records)\n    missing = calculate_missing_days(records, 'back')\n    \n    max_freq = max(back_freq.values()) if back_freq else 1\n    max_missing = max(missing.values()) if missing else 1\n    \n    scores = {}\n    for ball in range(1, 13):\n        freq_score = back_freq.get(ball, 0) / max_freq\n        missing_score = missing.get(ball, 0) / max_missing\n        scores[ball] = freq_score * 0.4 + missing_score * 0.6\n    \n    sorted_balls = sorted(scores.items(), key=lambda x: x[1], reverse=True)\n    return [ball for ball, score in sorted_balls[:count]]\n\ndef print_prediction(title, front_balls, back_balls):\n    \"\"\"打印预测结果\"\"\"\n    print(f\"\\n{'='*50}\")\n    print(f\"📊 {title}\")\n    print(f\"{'='*50}\")\n    print(f\"🎱 前区号码: {' '.join(f'{b:02d}' for b in front_balls)}\")\n    print(f\"🔵 后区号码: {' '.join(f'{b:02d}' for b in back_balls)}\")\n    print(f\"{'='*50}\")\n\ndef print_statistics(records):\n    \"\"\"打印统计信息\"\"\"\n    print(f\"\\n{'='*50}\")\n    print(f\"📈 历史数据统计\")\n    print(f\"{'='*50}\")\n    \n    front_freq = analyze_front_balls(records)\n    back_freq = analyze_back_balls(records)\n    \n    print(f\"\\n🎱 前区号码频率 TOP 10:\")\n    for ball, freq in front_freq.most_common(10):\n        bar = '█' * freq\n        print(f\"   {ball:02d}: {bar} ({freq}次)\")\n    \n    print(f\"\\n🔵 后区号码频率:\")\n    for ball, freq in back_freq.most_common():\n        bar = '█' * freq\n        print(f\"   {ball:02d}: {bar} ({freq}次)\")\n    \n    print(f\"\\n📊 遗漏情况 (前区):\")\n    missing = calculate_missing_days(records, 'front')\n    sorted_missing = sorted(missing.items(), key=lambda x: x[1], reverse=True)[:10]\n    for ball, days in sorted_missing:\n        print(f\"   {ball:02d}: {days}期未出现\")\n\ndef main():\n    parser = argparse.ArgumentParser(description='大乐透预测模型')\n    parser.add_argument('--strategy', '-s', type=str, \n                       choices=['hot', 'cold', 'missing', 'balanced', 'ml', 'all'],\n                       default='all', help='预测策略')\n    parser.add_argument('--count', '-c', type=int, default=3, help='生成几组号码')\n    parser.add_argument('--history', type=int, default=None, help='使用最近多少期数据')\n    parser.add_argument('--stats', action='store_true', help='显示统计信息')\n    args = parser.parse_args()\n    \n    records = get_all_records(args.history)\n    \n    if not records:\n        print(\"❌ 数据库中没有数据，请先运行 fetch_history.py 抓取数据\")\n        return\n    \n    print(f\"\\n🎲 大乐透预测模型\")\n    print(f\"📈 数据来源: 最近 {len(records)} 期历史数据\")\n    \n    # 显示统计信息\n    if args.stats:\n        print_statistics(records)\n    \n    # 生成后区号码池\n    back_balls_pool = list(range(1, 13))\n    \n    if args.strategy == 'all':\n        # 生成多种策略的预测\n        strategies = [\n            ('🔥 热号策略 (高频号码)', 'hot'),\n            ('❄️ 冷号策略 (低频号码)', 'cold'),\n            ('📈 遗漏策略 (长未出现)', 'missing'),\n            ('⚖️ 均衡策略 (冷热混合)', 'balanced'),\n            ('🤖 ML加权策略 (频率+遗漏)', 'ml'),\n        ]\n        \n        for name, strategy in strategies:\n            for i in range(args.count):\n                if strategy == 'hot':\n                    front = generate_hot_number_prediction(records, 5)\n                elif strategy == 'cold':\n                    front = generate_cold_number_prediction(records, 5)\n                elif strategy == 'missing':\n                    front = generate_missing_prediction(records, 5)\n                elif strategy == 'balanced':\n                    front = generate_balanced_prediction(records)\n                else:\n                    front = generate_ml_style_prediction(records)\n                \n                back = generate_back_balls_prediction(records, 2)\n                title = f\"{name} 第{i+1}组\"\n                print_prediction(title, front, back)\n    else:\n        # 生成指定策略的预测\n        for i in range(args.count):\n            if args.strategy == 'hot':\n                front = generate_hot_number_prediction(records, 5)\n            elif args.strategy == 'cold':\n                front = generate_cold_number_prediction(records, 5)\n            elif args.strategy == 'missing':\n                front = generate_missing_prediction(records, 5)\n            elif args.strategy == 'balanced':\n                front = generate_balanced_prediction(records)\n            else:\n                front = generate_ml_style_prediction(records)\n            \n            back = generate_back_balls_prediction(records, 2)\n            title = f\"预测 第{i+1}组\"\n            print_prediction(title, front, back)\n    \n    # 打印统计信息\n    print(f\"\\n📊 历史数据统计 (前区)\")\n    front_freq = analyze_front_balls(records)\n    print(f\"   最热号码: {front_freq.most_common(3)}\")\n    print(f\"   最冷号码: {front_freq.most_common()[-3:]}\")\n\nif __name__ == '__main__':\n    main()\n","path":"/workspace/projects/workspace/skills/super-lotto/scripts/predict.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":780,"output":2757,"cacheRead":58235,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":61772,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778129286091,"responseId":"064b4c8623771f27796c9639c3db3a15"},{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"callfunctionqhj7us47sl4m1","toolName":"write","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully wrote 9829 bytes to /workspace/projects/workspace/skills/super-lotto/scripts/predict.py"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1778129315118},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在让我运行测试看看效果。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"callfunction8wrt5vnb64jh1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /workspace/projects/workspace/skills/super-lotto && python scripts/predict.py --stats"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":427,"output":62,"cacheRead":61371,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":61860,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778129315119,"responseId":"064b4ca3076a955147923094ca8e5e91"},{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"callfunction8wrt5vnb64jh1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🎲 大乐透预测模型\n📈 数据来源: 最近 31 期历史数据\n\n==================================================\n📈 历史数据统计\n==================================================\n\n🎱 前区号码频率 TOP 10:\n   26: █████████ (9次)\n   12: ███████ (7次)\n   09: ██████ (6次)\n   21: ██████ (6次)\n   13: ██████ (6次)\n   27: ██████ (6次)\n   08: ██████ (6次)\n   22: ██████ (6次)\n   29: ██████ (6次)\n   34: ██████ (6次)\n\n🔵 后区号码频率:\n   08: ████████ (8次)\n   07: ███████ (7次)\n   12: ███████ (7次)\n   01: ██████ (6次)\n   06: ██████ (6次)\n   05: ██████ (6次)\n   10: █████ (5次)\n   11: ████ (4次)\n   04: ████ (4次)\n   02: ███ (3次)\n   03: ███ (3次)\n   09: ███ (3次)\n\n📊 遗漏情况 (前区):\n   31: 30期未出现\n   10: 22期未出现\n   05: 16期未出现\n   30: 14期未出现\n   04: 13期未出现\n   16: 13期未出现\n   32: 12期未出现\n   25: 8期未出现\n   34: 8期未出现\n   02: 7期未出现\n\n==================================================\n📊 🔥 热号策略 (高频号码) 第1组\n==================================================\n🎱 前区号码: 26 12 09 21 13\n🔵 后区号码: 05 08\n==================================================\n\n==================================================\n📊 🔥 热号策略 (高频号码) 第2组\n==================================================\n🎱 前区号码: 26 12 09 21 13\n🔵 后区号码: 05 08\n==================================================\n\n==================================================\n📊 🔥 热号策略 (高频号码) 第3组\n==================================================\n🎱 前区号码: 26 12 09 21 13\n🔵 后区号码: 05 08\n==================================================\n\n==================================================\n📊 ❄️ 冷号策略 (低频号码) 第1组\n==================================================\n🎱 前区号码: 25 04 16 30 31\n🔵 后区号码: 05 08\n==================================================\n\n==================================================\n📊 ❄️ 冷号策略 (低频号码) 第2组\n==================================================\n🎱 前区号码: 25 04 16 30 31\n🔵 后区号码: 05 08\n==================================================\n\n==================================================\n📊 ❄️ 冷号策略 (低频号码) 第3组\n==================================================\n🎱 前区号码: 25 04 16 30 31\n🔵 后区号码: 05 08\n==================================================\n\n==================================================\n📊 📈 遗漏策略 (长未出现) 第1组\n==================================================\n🎱 前区号码: 31 10 05 30 04\n🔵 后区号码: 05 08\n==================================================\n\n==================================================\n📊 📈 遗漏策略 (长未出现) 第2组\n==================================================\n🎱 前区号码: 31 10 05 30 04\n🔵 后区号码: 05 08\n==================================================\n\n==================================================\n📊 📈 遗漏策略 (长未出现) 第3组\n==================================================\n🎱 前区号码: 31 10 05 30 04\n🔵 后区号码: 05 08\n==================================================\n\n==================================================\n📊 ⚖️ 均衡策略 (冷热混合) 第1组\n==================================================\n🎱 前区号码: 10 12 18 26 31\n🔵 后区号码: 05 08\n==================================================\n\n==================================================\n📊 ⚖️ 均衡策略 (冷热混合) 第2组\n==================================================\n🎱 前区号码: 10 12 25 26 31\n🔵 后区号码: 05 08\n==================================================\n\n==================================================\n📊 ⚖️ 均衡策略 (冷热混合) 第3组\n==================================================\n🎱 前区号码: 10 12 26 27 31\n🔵 后区号码: 05 08\n==================================================\n\n==================================================\n📊 🤖 ML加权策略 (频率+遗漏) 第1组\n==================================================\n🎱 前区号码: 10 31 05 26 12\n🔵 后区号码: 05 08\n==================================================\n\n==================================================\n📊 🤖 ML加权策略 (频率+遗漏) 第2组\n==================================================\n🎱 前区号码: 10 31 05 26 12\n🔵 后区号码: 05 08\n==================================================\n\n==================================================\n📊 🤖 ML加权策略 (频率+遗漏) 第3组\n==================================================\n🎱 前区号码: 10 31 05 26 12\n🔵 后区号码: 05 08\n==================================================\n\n📊 历史数据统计 (前区)\n   最热号码: [(26, 9), (12, 7), (9, 6)]\n   最冷号码: [(16, 3), (30, 2), (31, 1)]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1778129317847},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"太棒了！预测模型已经可以正常工作了！现在让我更新 SKILL.md 文件，添加预测功能说明。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n预测模型运行成功！现在更新技能文档：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"callfunction2h6sa5sxm6591","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/workspace/projects/workspace/skills/super-lotto/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":5353,"output":98,"cacheRead":57787,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":63238,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778129317849,"responseId":"064b4ca657b4a055d424ff99e734334c"},{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"callfunction2h6sa5sxm6591","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: super-lotto\ndescription: 大乐透历史数据抓取、存储和分析技能。用于查询彩票500万网站、抓取历史开奖数据（前区红球+后区蓝球）、存储到本地数据库、并进行数据分析和频率统计。触发词：大乐透、彩票、开奖、彩票预测、历史数据、中奖号码、彩票分析、超级大乐透。\n---\n\n# 大乐透数据抓取与分析\n\n## 概述\n\n此技能提供大乐透历史开奖数据的抓取、存储和查询分析能力。支持从彩票500万网站抓取历史数据，存储到本地SQLite数据库，并提供频率分析、号码统计等功能。\n\n## 快速开始\n\n### 1. 初始化数据库\n\n```bash\npython scripts/init_db.py\n```\n\n### 2. 抓取历史数据\n\n```bash\n# 从彩票500万网站抓取数据\npython scripts/fetch_history.py\n```\n\n### 3. 查询数据\n\n```bash\n# 查看最新10期开奖\npython scripts/query.py latest\n\n# 查看最新50期\npython scripts/query.py latest 50\n\n# 按期号查询\npython scripts/query.py issue 26048\n\n# 按日期范围查询\npython scripts/query.py date 2024-01-01 2024-12-31\n\n# 号码频率分析（最近100期）\npython scripts/query.py analyze\n\n# 分析最近200期\npython scripts/query.py analyze 200\n\n# 数据统计\npython scripts/query.py stats\n```\n\n## 数据结构\n\n详细数据结构见 `references/data_structure.md`\n\n### 数据库表：lottery_records\n\n- **issue_number**: 期号（如 26048，表示2026年第48期）\n- **draw_date**: 开奖日期\n- **front_ball_1 到 front_ball_5**: 前区（红球）号码（1-35）\n- **back_ball_1, back_ball_2**: 后区（蓝球）号码（1-12）\n\n## 使用场景\n\n### 场景1：抓取最新数据\n\n用户：\"帮我抓取大乐透最新开奖数据\"\n\n操作步骤：\n1. 运行 `python scripts/fetch_history.py`\n2. 数据会自动保存到本地数据库\n3. 使用 `python scripts/query.py latest` 查看结果\n\n### 场景2：查询历史记录\n\n用户：\"查一下最近30期的开奖结果\"\n\n```bash\npython scripts/query.py latest 30\n```\n\n### 场景3：号码频率分析\n\n用户：\"分析一下最近100期哪些号码出现最多\"\n\n```bash\npython scripts/query.py analyze 100\n```\n\n会输出：\n- 前区（红球）出现频率 TOP 10\n- 后区（蓝球）出现频率 TOP 5\n- 热号（高频号码）\n- 冷号（低频号码）\n\n### 场景4：特定日期查询\n\n用户：\"查一下2024年1月到3月的开奖记录\"\n\n```bash\npython scripts/query.py date 2024-01-01 2024-03-31\n```\n\n## 大乐透规则\n\n- **前区（红球）**：从 01-35 中选择 5 个不重复的号码\n- **后区（蓝球）**：从 01-12 中选择 2 个号码\n- **开奖频率**：每周一、三、六\n\n## 数据源\n\n### 彩票500万网\n\n- **URL**: https://datachart.500.com/dlt/history/newinc/history.php\n- **优势**: 数据准确，更新及时\n- **格式**: HTML表格\n- **支持**: 查看最近30期、50期、100期\n\n## 工作流程\n\n```\n┌─────────────┐\n│ 初始化数据库 │ → python scripts/init_db.py\n└──────┬──────┘\n       │\n       ▼\n┌─────────────┐\n│  抓取数据    │ → python scripts/fetch_history.py\n└──────┬──────┘\n       │\n       ▼\n┌─────────────┐\n│  查询分析    │ → python scripts/query.py [命令]\n└─────────────┘\n```\n\n## 注意事项\n\n1. **依赖安装**: 需要安装 playwright (`pip install playwright`)\n2. **首次运行**: 需要运行 `playwright install chromium` 安装浏览器\n3. **网络连接**: 抓取数据需要稳定的网络连接\n4. **数据更新**: 建议定期运行抓取脚本更新数据\n5. **数据备份**: 数据库文件位于 `data/super_lotto.db`，可定期备份\n\n## 脚本说明\n\n### init_db.py\n\n- 初始化SQLite数据库\n- 创建表结构和索引\n- 数据库路径: `data/super_lotto.db`\n\n### fetch_history.py\n\n- 使用Playwright从彩票500万网站抓取数据\n- 自动解析HTML表格\n- 支持增量更新\n\n### query.py\n\n- 提供多种查询功能\n- 支持频率分析\n- 支持热号/冷号统计\n\n## 与双色球的区别\n\n| 彩票类型 | 前区（红球） | 后区（蓝球） |\n|---------|------------|------------|\n| 双色球 | 6个（1-33） | 1个（1-16） |\n| 大乐透 | 5个（1-35） | 2个（1-12） |\n\n## 扩展建议\n\n此技能可扩展为：\n- 添加预测模型（基于历史数据）\n- 添加可视化图表\n- 添加自动定时更新\n- 添加中奖查询功能\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1778129322055},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我需要更新 SKILL.md 文件，添加预测模型的说明。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"callfunctionxqve4medz43e1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"---\nname: super-lotto\ndescription: 大乐透历史数据抓取、存储和分析技能。用于查询彩票500万网站、抓取历史开奖数据（前区红球+后区蓝球）、存储到本地数据库、进行数据分析和频率统计、生成号码预测。触发词：大乐透、彩票、开奖、彩票预测、历史数据、中奖号码、彩票分析、超级大乐透、大乐透预测。\n---\n\n# 大乐透数据抓取与分析预测\n\n## 概述\n\n此技能提供大乐透历史开奖数据的抓取、存储、查询分析和号码预测能力。支持从彩票500万网站抓取历史数据，存储到本地SQLite数据库，提供频率分析、热冷号统计，并基于多种策略生成预测号码。\n\n## 快速开始\n\n### 1. 初始化数据库（首次使用）\n\n```bash\npython scripts/init_db.py\n```\n\n### 2. 抓取历史数据\n\n```bash\npython scripts/fetch_history.py\n```\n\n### 3. 生成预测\n\n```bash\n# 生成所有策略的预测（推荐）\npython scripts/predict.py\n\n# 查看详细统计\npython scripts/predict.py --stats\n\n# 生成3组热号策略预测\npython scripts/predict.py --strategy hot --count 3\n\n# 使用最近50期数据预测\npython scripts/predict.py --history 50\n```\n\n### 4. 查询数据\n\n```bash\n# 查看最新10期开奖\npython scripts/query.py latest\n\n# 查看最新50期\npython scripts/query.py latest 50\n\n# 号码频率分析\npython scripts/query.py analyze\n```\n\n## 预测模型\n\n### 预测策略\n\n| 策略 | 说明 | 适用场景 |\n|------|------|----------|\n| 🔥 热号策略 | 选择历史出现频率最高的号码 | 追热号 |\n| ❄️ 冷号策略 | 选择历史出现频率最低的号码 | 追冷号 |\n| 📈 遗漏策略 | 选择很久未出现的号码 | 追遗漏 |\n| ⚖️ 均衡策略 | 热号+冷号+遗漏混合 | 平衡风险 |\n| 🤖 ML加权策略 | 频率40%+遗漏60%加权评分 | 智能推荐 |\n\n### 预测命令\n\n```bash\n# 生成1组预测（默认所有策略）\npython scripts/predict.py\n\n# 生成5组热号预测\npython scripts/predict.py --strategy hot --count 5\n\n# 生成5组冷号预测\npython scripts/predict.py --strategy cold --count 5\n\n# 生成5组遗漏策略预测\npython scripts/predict.py --strategy missing --count 5\n\n# 生成5组均衡策略预测\npython scripts/predict.py --strategy balanced --count 5\n\n# 生成5组ML加权策略预测\npython scripts/predict.py --strategy ml --count 5\n\n# 显示详细统计信息\npython scripts/predict.py --stats\n\n# 使用最近100期数据预测\npython scripts/predict.py --history 100\n```\n\n## 使用场景\n\n### 场景1：获取最新预测\n\n用户：\"大乐透预测\"\n\n操作步骤：\n1. 运行 `python scripts/predict.py`\n2. 选择喜欢的策略组合\n\n### 场景2：查看统计信息\n\n用户：\"分析一下大乐透的热号冷号\"\n\n操作步骤：\n```bash\npython scripts/predict.py --stats\n```\n\n会输出：\n- 前区号码频率柱状图 TOP 10\n- 后区号码频率柱状图\n- 遗漏排行榜（前区）\n\n### 场景3：抓取最新数据\n\n用户：\"帮我更新大乐透数据\"\n\n操作步骤：\n```bash\npython scripts/fetch_history.py\n```\n\n## 大乐透规则\n\n- **前区（红球）**：从 01-35 中选择 5 个不重复的号码\n- **后区（蓝球）**：从 01-12 中选择 2 个号码\n- **开奖频率**：每周一、三、六\n\n## 数据源\n\n### 彩票500万网\n\n- **URL**: https://datachart.500.com/dlt/history/newinc/history.php\n- **优势**: 数据准确，更新及时\n\n## 工作流程\n\n```\n┌─────────────┐\n│ 初始化数据库 │ → python scripts/init_db.py\n└──────┬──────┘\n       │\n       ▼\n┌─────────────┐\n│  抓取数据    │ → python scripts/fetch_history.py\n└──────┬──────┘\n       │\n       ▼\n┌─────────────┐\n│  预测分析    │ → python scripts/predict.py\n└─────────────┘\n```\n\n## 脚本说明\n\n### predict.py（新增）\n\n- 基于历史数据的多策略预测模型\n- 支持5种预测策略\n- 生成频率统计和遗漏分析\n- 后区号码智能推荐\n\n### init_db.py\n\n- 初始化SQLite数据库\n- 创建表结构和索引\n\n### fetch_history.py\n\n- 使用Playwright从彩票500万网站抓取数据\n- 支持增量更新\n\n### query.py\n\n- 提供多种查询功能\n- 支持频率分析\n\n## 数据库表：lottery_records\n\n| 字段 | 类型 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|\n| id | INTEGER | 主键 |\n| issue_number | TEXT | 期号（如 26048） |\n| draw_date | DATE | 开奖日期 |\n| front_ball_1~5 | INTEGER | 前区号码（1-35） |\n| back_ball_1~2 | INTEGER | 后区号码（1-12） |\n\n## ⚠️ 免责声明\n\n彩票开奖是完全随机的概率事件，历史数据分析和任何预测模型都无法保证中奖。本技能提供的预测仅供参考娱乐，请理性购彩，量力而行。\n\n## 与双色球的区别\n\n| 彩票类型 | 前区（红球） | 后区（蓝球） |\n|---------|------------|------------|\n| 双色球 | 6个（1-33） | 1个（1-16） |\n| 大乐透 | 5个（1-35） | 2个（1-12） |\n","path":"/workspace/projects/workspace/skills/super-lotto/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":1210,"output":1354,"cacheRead":63163,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":65727,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778129322056,"responseId":"064b4caaaccab1cd7ba62b8ae2fdc081"},{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"callfunctionxqve4medz43e1","toolName":"write","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully wrote 3001 bytes to /workspace/projects/workspace/skills/super-lotto/SKILL.md"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1778129341112},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我已经完成了：\n1. 创建了预测脚本 predict.py\n2. 更新了 SKILL.md 文档\n\n让我给用户展示一下预测结果，并总结一下功能。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"🎉 **大乐透预测模型已创建完成！**\n\n## 预测功能概览\n\n### 支持 5 种预测策略\n\n| 策略 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| 🔥 **热号策略** | 选择历史出现频率最高的号码 |\n| ❄️ **冷号策略** | 选择历史出现频率最低的号码 |\n| 📈 **遗漏策略** | 选择很久未出现的号码 |\n| ⚖️ **均衡策略** | 热号+冷号+遗漏混合搭配 |\n| 🤖 **ML加权策略** | 频率40%+遗漏60%加权评分 |\n\n### 使用方式\n\n```bash\n# 生成所有策略的预测\npython scripts/predict.py\n\n# 显示详细统计\npython scripts/predict.py --stats\n\n# 指定策略和数量\npython scripts/predict.py --strategy ml --count 5\n```\n\n### 当前数据统计（最近31期）\n\n**🔥 前区热号 TOP 5:**\n- 26 号：出现 9 次\n- 12 号：出现 7 次\n- 09/21/13 号：各出现 6 次\n\n**❄️ 前区冷号（遗漏很久）:**\n- 31 号：30期未出现\n- 10 号：22期未出现\n- 05 号：16期未出现\n\n**🔵 后区热号:** 08、07、12 号最活跃\n\n---\n\n⚠️ **温馨提示：** 彩票开奖是完全随机的概率事件，历史数据分析仅供参考娱乐，请理性购彩！🍀"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":345,"output":396,"cacheRead":65403,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":66144,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778129341113,"responseId":"064b4cbdde432d114341dd2e7115dacb"},{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_f70eb83737eac4282ce8bee3202593c7\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b50f58e0a3cb4b399e54d7c5cf9a\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_f70eb83737eac4282ce8bee3202593c7\",\n  \"sender\": \"haidong\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Thu 2026-05-07 12:58 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"haidong (ou_f70eb83737eac4282ce8bee3202593c7)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_f70eb83737eac4282ce8bee3202593c7\",\n  \"name\": \"haidong\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b50f58e0a3cb4b399e54d7c5cf9a]\nhaidong: 创建双色球预测模型"}],"timestamp":1778129934490},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想要创建双色球预测模型。我有一个双色球技能（double-color-ball），让我先看看它的当前状态，然后为它添加预测功能。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_u2u27cx1ehup_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/workspace/projects/workspace/skills/double-color-ball/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":65478,"output":99,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":65577,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778129934493,"responseId":"064b4f0ef605e6cdfa542ff7cd490304"},{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_u2u27cx1ehup_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: double-color-ball\ndescription: 双色球历史数据抓取、存储和分析技能。用于查询彩票网站、抓取历史开奖数据（红球+蓝球）、存储到本地数据库、并进行数据分析和频率统计。触发词：双色球、彩票、开奖、彩票预测、历史数据、中奖号码、彩票分析。\n---\n\n# 双色球数据抓取与分析\n\n## 概述\n\n此技能提供双色球历史开奖数据的抓取、存储和查询分析能力。支持从官方彩票网站抓取完整历史数据，存储到本地SQLite数据库，并提供频率分析、号码统计等功能。\n\n## 快速开始\n\n### 1. 初始化数据库\n\n```bash\npython scripts/init_db.py\n```\n\n### 2. 抓取历史数据\n\n```bash\n# 使用官方数据源（推荐）\npython scripts/fetch_history.py cwl\n\n# 使用500彩票网数据源\npython scripts/fetch_history.py 500com\n```\n\n### 3. 查询数据\n\n```bash\n# 查看最新10期开奖\npython scripts/query.py latest\n\n# 查看最新50期\npython scripts/query.py latest 50\n\n# 按期号查询\npython scripts/query.py issue 2024001\n\n# 按日期范围查询\npython scripts/query.py date 2024-01-01 2024-12-31\n\n# 号码频率分析（最近100期）\npython scripts/query.py analyze\n\n# 分析最近200期\npython scripts/query.py analyze 200\n\n# 数据统计\npython scripts/query.py stats\n```\n\n## 数据结构\n\n详细数据结构见 `references/data_structure.md`\n\n### 数据库表：lottery_records\n\n- **issue_number**: 期号（如 2024001）\n- **draw_date**: 开奖日期\n- **red_ball_1 到 red_ball_6**: 红球号码（1-33）\n- **blue_ball**: 蓝球号码（1-16）\n\n## 使用场景\n\n### 场景1：抓取最新数据\n\n用户：\"帮我抓取双色球最新开奖数据\"\n\n操作步骤：\n1. 运行 `python scripts/fetch_history.py cwl`\n2. 数据会自动保存到本地数据库\n3. 使用 `python scripts/query.py latest` 查看结果\n\n### 场景2：查询历史记录\n\n用户：\"查一下最近30期的开奖结果\"\n\n```bash\npython scripts/query.py latest 30\n```\n\n### 场景3：号码频率分析\n\n用户：\"分析一下最近100期哪些号码出现最多\"\n\n```bash\npython scripts/query.py analyze 100\n```\n\n会输出：\n- 红球出现频率 TOP 10\n- 蓝球出现频率 TOP 5\n- 热号（高频号码）\n- 冷号（低频号码）\n\n### 场景4：特定日期查询\n\n用户：\"查一下2024年1月到3月的开奖记录\"\n\n```bash\npython scripts/query.py date 2024-01-01 2024-03-31\n```\n\n## 数据源\n\n### 中国福利彩票网（推荐）\n\n- **URL**: https://www.cwl.gov.cn\n- **优势**: 官方数据源，准确可靠\n- **格式**: JSON API\n- **支持**: 分页查询，可获取全部历史数据\n\n### 500彩票网\n\n- **URL**: https://datachart.500.com\n- **优势**: 第三方数据源\n- **格式**: HTML解析\n- **支持**: 批量查询\n\n## 工作流程\n\n```\n┌─────────────┐\n│ 初始化数据库 │ → python scripts/init_db.py\n└──────┬──────┘\n       │\n       ▼\n┌─────────────┐\n│  抓取数据    │ → python scripts/fetch_history.py cwl\n└──────┬──────┘\n       │\n       ▼\n┌─────────────┐\n│  查询分析    │ → python scripts/query.py [命令]\n└─────────────┘\n```\n\n## 注意事项\n\n1. **网络连接**: 抓取数据需要稳定的网络连接\n2. **请求频率**: 脚本内置了请求间隔，避免被网站封禁\n3. **数据更新**: 建议定期运行抓取脚本更新数据\n4. **数据备份**: 数据库文件位于 `data/double_color_ball.db`，可定期备份\n\n## 脚本说明\n\n### init_db.py\n\n- 初始化SQLite数据库\n- 创建表结构和索引\n- 数据库路径: `data/double_color_ball.db`\n\n### fetch_history.py\n\n- 从彩票网站抓取历史数据\n- 支持多个数据源（cwl, 500com）\n- 自动去重，增量更新\n- 支持分页抓取全部数据\n\n### query.py\n\n- 提供多种查询功能\n- 支持频率分析\n- 支持热号/冷号统计\n\n## 扩展建议\n\n此技能可扩展为：\n- 添加预测模型（基于历史数据）\n- 添加可视化图表\n- 添加自动定时更新\n- 添加中奖查询功能\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1778129939141},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，双色球技能已有数据抓取和分析功能。让我检查一下当前的数据状态，然后创建预测模型脚本。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_cswg1arzh0dq_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /workspace/projects/workspace/skills/double-color-ball && ls -la scripts/ data/ 2>/dev/null"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_cswg1arzh0dq_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /workspace/projects/workspace/skills/double-color-ball && python -c \"\nimport sqlite3\nconn = sqlite3.connect('data/double_color_ball.db')\ncursor = conn.cursor()\ncursor.execute('SELECT COUNT(*) FROM lottery_records')\nprint(f'总记录数: {cursor.fetchone()[0]}')\ncursor.execute('SELECT * FROM lottery_records ORDER BY issue_number DESC LIMIT 3')\nrows = cursor.fetchall()\nprint('\\n最新3期开奖:')\nfor row in rows:\n    print(f'期号: {row[1]}, 日期: {row[2]}, 红球: {row[3:9]}, 蓝球: {row[9]}')\nconn.close()\n\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"需要初始化数据库\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":1186,"output":275,"cacheRead":65403,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":66864,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778129939142,"responseId":"064b4f131ecdd8861bc0