{"traceSchema":"openclaw-trajectory","schemaVersion":1,"traceId":"2cd6a4e0-f5f2-4c1e-8f10-f0c388994467","source":"runtime","type":"model.completed","ts":"2026-05-07T05:13:37.026Z","seq":5,"sourceSeq":5,"sessionId":"2cd6a4e0-f5f2-4c1e-8f10-f0c388994467","sessionKey":"agent:main:main","runId":"38e7bec9-cb36-4e73-ade5-0a02e4ebaa7a","workspaceDir":"/workspace/projects/workspace","provider":"coze","modelId":"auto","modelApi":"openai-completions","data":{"aborted":false,"externalAbort":false,"timedOut":false,"idleTimedOut":false,"timedOutDuringCompaction":false,"promptErrorSource":null,"usage":{"input":74497,"output":608,"cacheRead":74363,"total":149468},"promptCache":{"lastCallUsage":{"input":323,"output":252,"cacheRead":74363,"cacheWrite":0,"total":74938},"lastCacheTouchAt":1778130810684},"compactionCount":0,"assistantTexts":["🍀 **双色球推荐号码（均衡策略）**\n\n| 类型 | 号码 |\n|------|------|\n| 🔴 **红球** | 05 06 14 21 26 28 |\n| 🔵 **蓝球** | 09 |\n\n---\n\n**推荐理由（均衡策略）：**\n- 2个热号：06、14（历史高频）\n- 2个遗漏号：05（33期未出）、26（23期未出）\n- 2个冷号：21、28（历史低频）\n\n**仅供参考娱乐，祝你好运！** 🎰"],"finalPromptText":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_f70eb83737eac4282ce8bee3202593c7\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b50f5b82c40bcb4c4a201133cfbb\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_f70eb83737eac4282ce8bee3202593c7\",\n  \"sender\": \"haidong\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Thu 2026-05-07 13:13 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"haidong (ou_f70eb83737eac4282ce8bee3202593c7)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_f70eb83737eac4282ce8bee3202593c7\",\n  \"name\": \"haidong\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b50f5b82c40bcb4c4a201133cfbb]\nhaidong: 这个结果不对，双色球前区是6个号码，预测模型要基于双色球技能的数据库来预测，再次预测","messagesSnapshot":[{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_f70eb83737eac4282ce8bee3202593c7\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b50f5df7cd4b8c45216bb251d089\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_f70eb83737eac4282ce8bee3202593c7\",\n  \"sender\": \"haidong\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Thu 2026-05-07 12:46 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"haidong (ou_f70eb83737eac4282ce8bee3202593c7)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_f70eb83737eac4282ce8bee3202593c7\",\n  \"name\": \"haidong\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b50f5df7cd4b8c45216bb251d089]\nhaidong: 创建大乐透预测模型"}],"timestamp":1778129181007},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想要创建大乐透预测模型。我看到有一个相关的 skill 叫做 \"super-lotto\"，描述是：大乐透历史数据抓取、存储和分析技能。用于查询彩票500万网站、抓取历史开奖数据（前区红球+后区蓝球）、存储到本地数据库、并进行数据分析和频率统计。触发词：大乐透、彩票、开奖、彩票预测、历史数据、中奖号码、彩票分析、超级大乐透。\n\n这个 skill 正好匹配用户的需求，我应该先读取这个 skill 的 SKILL.md 文件来了解如何使用它。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"callfunction8rquq3nlt0yq1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/workspace/projects/workspace/skills/super-lotto/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":47404,"output":273,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":47677,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778129181010,"responseId":"064b4c1d4298a0860e6f3c9d976129de"},{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"callfunction8rquq3nlt0yq1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: super-lotto\ndescription: 大乐透历史数据抓取、存储和分析技能。用于查询彩票500万网站、抓取历史开奖数据（前区红球+后区蓝球）、存储到本地数据库、并进行数据分析和频率统计。触发词：大乐透、彩票、开奖、彩票预测、历史数据、中奖号码、彩票分析、超级大乐透。\n---\n\n# 大乐透数据抓取与分析\n\n## 概述\n\n此技能提供大乐透历史开奖数据的抓取、存储和查询分析能力。支持从彩票500万网站抓取历史数据，存储到本地SQLite数据库，并提供频率分析、号码统计等功能。\n\n## 快速开始\n\n### 1. 初始化数据库\n\n```bash\npython scripts/init_db.py\n```\n\n### 2. 抓取历史数据\n\n```bash\n# 从彩票500万网站抓取数据\npython scripts/fetch_history.py\n```\n\n### 3. 查询数据\n\n```bash\n# 查看最新10期开奖\npython scripts/query.py latest\n\n# 查看最新50期\npython scripts/query.py latest 50\n\n# 按期号查询\npython scripts/query.py issue 26048\n\n# 按日期范围查询\npython scripts/query.py date 2024-01-01 2024-12-31\n\n# 号码频率分析（最近100期）\npython scripts/query.py analyze\n\n# 分析最近200期\npython scripts/query.py analyze 200\n\n# 数据统计\npython scripts/query.py stats\n```\n\n## 数据结构\n\n详细数据结构见 `references/data_structure.md`\n\n### 数据库表：lottery_records\n\n- **issue_number**: 期号（如 26048，表示2026年第48期）\n- **draw_date**: 开奖日期\n- **front_ball_1 到 front_ball_5**: 前区（红球）号码（1-35）\n- **back_ball_1, back_ball_2**: 后区（蓝球）号码（1-12）\n\n## 使用场景\n\n### 场景1：抓取最新数据\n\n用户：\"帮我抓取大乐透最新开奖数据\"\n\n操作步骤：\n1. 运行 `python scripts/fetch_history.py`\n2. 数据会自动保存到本地数据库\n3. 使用 `python scripts/query.py latest` 查看结果\n\n### 场景2：查询历史记录\n\n用户：\"查一下最近30期的开奖结果\"\n\n```bash\npython scripts/query.py latest 30\n```\n\n### 场景3：号码频率分析\n\n用户：\"分析一下最近100期哪些号码出现最多\"\n\n```bash\npython scripts/query.py analyze 100\n```\n\n会输出：\n- 前区（红球）出现频率 TOP 10\n- 后区（蓝球）出现频率 TOP 5\n- 热号（高频号码）\n- 冷号（低频号码）\n\n### 场景4：特定日期查询\n\n用户：\"查一下2024年1月到3月的开奖记录\"\n\n```bash\npython scripts/query.py date 2024-01-01 2024-03-31\n```\n\n## 大乐透规则\n\n- **前区（红球）**：从 01-35 中选择 5 个不重复的号码\n- **后区（蓝球）**：从 01-12 中选择 2 个号码\n- **开奖频率**：每周一、三、六\n\n## 数据源\n\n### 彩票500万网\n\n- **URL**: https://datachart.500.com/dlt/history/newinc/history.php\n- **优势**: 数据准确，更新及时\n- **格式**: HTML表格\n- **支持**: 查看最近30期、50期、100期\n\n## 工作流程\n\n```\n┌─────────────┐\n│ 初始化数据库 │ → python scripts/init_db.py\n└──────┬──────┘\n       │\n       ▼\n┌─────────────┐\n│  抓取数据    │ → python scripts/fetch_history.py\n└──────┬──────┘\n       │\n       ▼\n┌─────────────┐\n│  查询分析    │ → python scripts/query.py [命令]\n└─────────────┘\n```\n\n## 注意事项\n\n1. **依赖安装**: 需要安装 playwright (`pip install playwright`)\n2. **首次运行**: 需要运行 `playwright install chromium` 安装浏览器\n3. **网络连接**: 抓取数据需要稳定的网络连接\n4. **数据更新**: 建议定期运行抓取脚本更新数据\n5. **数据备份**: 数据库文件位于 `data/super_lotto.db`，可定期备份\n\n## 脚本说明\n\n### init_db.py\n\n- 初始化SQLite数据库\n- 创建表结构和索引\n- 数据库路径: `data/super_lotto.db`\n\n### fetch_history.py\n\n- 使用Playwright从彩票500万网站抓取数据\n- 自动解析HTML表格\n- 支持增量更新\n\n### query.py\n\n- 提供多种查询功能\n- 支持频率分析\n- 支持热号/冷号统计\n\n## 与双色球的区别\n\n| 彩票类型 | 前区（红球） | 后区（蓝球） |\n|---------|------------|------------|\n| 双色球 | 6个（1-33） | 1个（1-16） |\n| 大乐透 | 5个（1-35） | 2个（1-12） |\n\n## 扩展建议\n\n此技能可扩展为：\n- 添加预测模型（基于历史数据）\n- 添加可视化图表\n- 添加自动定时更新\n- 添加中奖查询功能\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1778129186251},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"这是一个大乐透数据抓取和分析的技能。用户想要创建\"预测模型\"，这个技能主要是做数据抓取和频率分析，没有真正的预测模型。\n\n让我先检查一下这个技能的目录结构，看看有哪些脚本可用，以及是否可以基于现有数据来构建预测模型。\n\n我应该：\n1. 先检查数据库是否已有数据\n2. 运行抓取脚本获取最新数据\n3. 基于频率分析结果，提供一个简单的预测\n\n但实际上，彩票是随机开奖的，没有真正的预测方法。真正的\"预测模型\"只是基于历史数据的统计分析，给出一些参考号码。我应该向用户说明这一点，并提供一个基于频率分析的简单\"推荐\"功能。\n\n让我先检查一下现有的脚本和数据库状态。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的，我来帮你创建大乐透预测模型！这个技能已经具备数据抓取和频率分析能力，我来检查一下当前状态，然后为你构建预测功能。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"callfunction897nsg4zp1uc1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /workspace/projects/workspace/skills/super-lotto && ls -la"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"callfunction897nsg4zp1uc2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /workspace/projects/workspace/skills/super-lotto && ls -la scripts/ data/ 2>/dev/null || echo \"目录不存在\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":1237,"output":407,"cacheRead":47483,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":49127,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778129186251,"responseId":"064b4c22180c2b3c9541c00d91201dd9"},{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"callfunction897nsg4zp1uc1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"total 28\ndrwxr-xr-x 5 root root 4096 May  6 21:26 .\ndrwxr-xr-x 9 root root 4096 May  6 21:22 ..\ndrwxr-xr-x 2 root root 4096 May  6 21:28 data\ndrwxr-xr-x 2 root root 4096 May  6 21:25 references\ndrwxr-xr-x 2 root root 4096 May  6 21:25 scripts\n-rw-r--r-- 1 root root 4499 May  6 21:26 SKILL.md"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1778129193912},{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"callfunction897nsg4zp1uc2","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"data/:\ntotal 32\ndrwxr-xr-x 2 root root  4096 May  6 21:28 .\ndrwxr-xr-x 5 root root  4096 May  6 21:26 ..\n-rw-r--r-- 1 root root 24576 May  6 21:28 super_lotto.db\n\nscripts/:\ntotal 28\ndrwxr-xr-x 2 root root 4096 May  6 21:25 .\ndrwxr-xr-x 5 root root 4096 May  6 21:26 ..\n-rw-r--r-- 1 root root 7568 May  6 21:28 fetch_history.py\n-rw-r--r-- 1 root root 2108 May  6 21:23 init_db.py\n-rw-r--r-- 1 root root 8140 May  6 21:30 query.py"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1778129193912},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，数据库已经存在。让我检查一下数据库里有多少条记录，以及抓取最新数据。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"数据库已有数据，让我抓取最新数据并分析当前状态：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"callfunctionrus4dmlv79pa1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /workspace/projects/workspace/skills/super-lotto && python scripts/fetch_history.py 2>&1 | head -50"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"callfunctionrus4dmlv79pa2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /workspace/projects/workspace/skills/super-lotto && sqlite3 data/super_lotto.db \"SELECT COUNT(*) as total_records FROM lottery_records;\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":507,"output":158,"cacheRead":48827,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":49492,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778129193913,"responseId":"064b4c2a073c50e98db9099c675dbeee"},{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"callfunctionrus4dmlv79pa1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"============================================================\n🎲 大乐透历史数据抓取\n============================================================\n\n📡 正在访问彩票500万网...\n   URL: https://datachart.500.com/dlt/history/newinc/history.php\n📊 正在解析数据...\n✅ 成功抓取 30 条记录\n/workspace/projects/workspace/skills/super-lotto/scripts/fetch_history.py:185: DeprecationWarning: The default date adapter is deprecated as of Python 3.12; see the sqlite3 documentation for suggested replacement recipes\n  cursor.execute('''\n/workspace/projects/workspace/skills/super-lotto/scripts/fetch_history.py:155: DeprecationWarning: The default date adapter is deprecated as of Python 3.12; see the sqlite3 documentation for suggested replacement recipes\n  cursor.execute('''\n✅ 数据保存完成: 新增 1 条, 更新 29 条\n\n✅ 总计保存 30 条记录"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1778129197784},{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"callfunctionrus4dmlv79pa2","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"/usr/bin/sh: 1: sqlite3: not found\n\nCommand not found"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1778129197784},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"抓取了30条数据，但是sqlite3命令行工具不存在。让我用Python来查询数据库。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"callfunctionw7y5iifi7qi71","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /workspace/projects/workspace/skills/super-lotto && python -c \"\nimport sqlite3\nconn = sqlite3.connect('data/super_lotto.db')\ncursor = conn.cursor()\ncursor.execute('SELECT COUNT(*) FROM lottery_records')\nprint(f'总记录数: {cursor.fetchone()[0]}')\ncursor.execute('SELECT * FROM lottery_records ORDER BY issue_number DESC LIMIT 5')\nrows = cursor.fetchall()\nprint('\\n最新5期开奖:')\nfor row in rows:\n    print(f'期号: {row[0]}, 日期: {row[1]}, 前区: {row[2:7]}, 后区: {row[7:9]}')\nconn.close()\n\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":417,"output":210,"cacheRead":49275,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":49902,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778129197785,"responseId":"064b4c2e26d478a6a08ed0f755a50cd9"},{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"callfunctionw7y5iifi7qi71","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"总记录数: 31\n\n最新5期开奖:\n期号: 31, 日期: 26049, 前区: ('2026-05-06', 1, 6, 14, 15), 后区: (17, 2)\n期号: 1, 日期: 26048, 前区: ('2026-05-04', 11, 17, 20, 23), 后区: (35, 1)\n期号: 2, 日期: 26047, 前区: ('2026-05-02', 9, 20, 21, 23), 后区: (28, 6)\n期号: 3, 日期: 26046, 前区: ('2026-04-29', 1, 13, 18, 27), 后区: (33, 4)\n期号: 4, 日期: 26045, 前区: ('2026-04-27', 1, 15, 21, 26), 后区: (33, 4)"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1778129201714},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，数据已经抓取完成。现在我需要创建一个预测模型脚本。这个脚本应该：\n\n1. 分析历史数据的频率统计\n2. 基于热号/冷号分析给出推荐号码\n3. 可以使用多种策略：\n   - 频率分析法（选择出现频率高的号码）\n   - 遗漏值分析法（选择很久没出现的号码）\n   - 随机组合法\n\n虽然彩票是随机开奖的，但我们可以提供基于统计分析的参考号码。我来创建一个预测脚本。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"数据已同步，共31期记录。现在我来创建预测模型：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"callfunctionj7aeypow1b511","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\n大乐透预测模型\n基于历史数据频率分析和遗漏值统计生成推荐号码\n\"\"\"\n\nimport sqlite3\nimport random\nfrom collections import Counter\nfrom datetime import datetime\nimport argparse\n\nDB_PATH = 'data/super_lotto.db'\n\ndef get_connection():\n    \"\"\"获取数据库连接\"\"\"\n    return sqlite3.connect(DB_PATH)\n\ndef get_all_records(limit=None):\n    \"\"\"获取所有开奖记录\"\"\"\n    conn = get_connection()\n    cursor = conn.cursor()\n    if limit:\n        cursor.execute(f'''\n            SELECT * FROM lottery_records \n            ORDER BY issue_number DESC \n            LIMIT {limit}\n        ''')\n    else:\n        cursor.execute('SELECT * FROM lottery_records ORDER BY issue_number DESC')\n    records = cursor.fetchall()\n    conn.close()\n    return records\n\ndef analyze_front_balls(records):\n    \"\"\"分析前区号码（红球 1-35）频率\"\"\"\n    front_balls = []\n    for record in records:\n        # 前区是 record[2:7] (去掉日期后的5个号码)\n        front_balls.extend(record[2:7])\n    return Counter(front_balls)\n\ndef analyze_back_balls(records):\n    \"\"\"分析后区号码（蓝球 1-12）频率\"\"\"\n    back_balls = []\n    for record in records:\n        # 后区是 record[7:9]\n        back_balls.extend(record[7:9])\n    return Counter(back_balls)\n\ndef calculate_missing_days(records, ball_type='front'):\n    \"\"\"计算号码遗漏天数（距上次出现的期数）\"\"\"\n    conn = get_connection()\n    cursor = conn.cursor()\n    \n    if ball_type == 'front':\n        max_ball = 35\n        columns = 'front_ball_1, front_ball_2, front_ball_3, front_ball_4, front_ball_5'\n    else:\n        max_ball = 12\n        columns = 'back_ball_1, back_ball_2'\n    \n    cursor.execute(f'''\n        SELECT issue_number FROM lottery_records \n        ORDER BY issue_number DESC\n    ''')\n    issues = [row[0] for row in cursor.fetchall()]\n    latest_issue = issues[0] if issues else 0\n    \n    missing_days = {}\n    for ball in range(1, max_ball + 1):\n        cursor.execute(f'''\n            SELECT issue_number FROM lottery_records \n            WHERE {columns} LIKE '%{ball}%'\n            ORDER BY issue_number DESC\n            LIMIT 1\n        ''')\n        result = cursor.fetchone()\n        if result:\n            missing_days[ball] = latest_issue - result[0]\n        else:\n            missing_days[ball] = latest_issue  # 从未出现\n    \n    conn.close()\n    return missing_days\n\ndef generate_hot_number_prediction(records, count=5):\n    \"\"\"基于热号生成预测（前区）\"\"\"\n    front_freq = analyze_front_balls(records)\n    # 选择出现频率最高的号码\n    hot_balls = front_freq.most_common(count)\n    return [ball for ball, freq in hot_balls]\n\ndef generate_cold_number_prediction(records, count=5):\n    \"\"\"基于冷号生成预测（前区）\"\"\"\n    front_freq = analyze_front_balls(records)\n    # 找出所有号码\n    all_balls = set(range(1, 36))\n    appeared = set(front_freq.keys())\n    never_appeared = all_balls - appeared\n    \n    # 选择出现次数最少的号码\n    cold_balls = front_freq.most_common()[-count:] if len(front_freq) >= count else []\n    return [ball for ball, freq in cold_balls] + list(never_appeared)[:count-len(cold_balls)-len(never_appeared)]\n\ndef generate_missing_prediction(records, count=5):\n    \"\"\"基于遗漏值生成预测（前区）\"\"\"\n    missing = calculate_missing_days(records, 'front')\n    # 选择遗漏值最大的号码\n    sorted_missing = sorted(missing.items(), key=lambda x: x[1], reverse=True)\n    return [ball for ball, days in sorted_missing[:count]]\n\ndef generate_random_prediction(count=5, ball_range=(1, 35)):\n    \"\"\"生成随机号码\"\"\"\n    return sorted(random.sample(range(ball_range[0], ball_range[1] + 1), count))\n\ndef generate_balanced_prediction(records):\n    \"\"\"生成均衡型预测（结合热号、冷号、随机）\"\"\"\n    # 2个热号\n    hot = generate_hot_number_prediction(records, 2)\n    # 1个冷号\n    cold = generate_cold_number_prediction(records, 1)\n    # 2个遗漏值大的号\n    missing = generate_missing_prediction(records, 2)\n    \n    # 合并并去重\n    combined = hot + cold + missing\n    seen = set()\n    result = []\n    for ball in combined:\n        if ball not in seen and len(result) < 5:\n            seen.add(ball)\n            result.append(ball)\n    \n    # 如果不够5个，随机补足\n    while len(result) < 5:\n        ball = random.randint(1, 35)\n        if ball not in seen:\n            seen.add(ball)\n            result.append(ball)\n    \n    return sorted(result)\n\ndef generate_ml_style_prediction(records):\n    \"\"\"基于加权评分的预测（模拟简单ML模型）\"\"\"\n    front_freq = analyze_front_balls(records)\n    missing = calculate_missing_days(records, 'front')\n    \n    # 计算每个号码的加权分数\n    max_freq = max(front_freq.values()) if front_freq else 1\n    max_missing = max(missing.values()) if missing else 1\n    \n    scores = {}\n    for ball in range(1, 36):\n        freq_score = front_freq.get(ball, 0) / max_freq  # 频率分数\n        missing_score = missing.get(ball, 0) / max_missing  # 遗漏分数\n        # 加权：频率占40%，遗漏占60%\n        scores[ball] = freq_score * 0.4 + missing_score * 0.6\n    \n    # 选择分数最高的5个号码\n    sorted_balls = sorted(scores.items(), key=lambda x: x[1], reverse=True)\n    return [ball for ball, score in sorted_balls[:5]]\n\ndef print_prediction(title, front_balls, back_balls):\n    \"\"\"打印预测结果\"\"\"\n    print(f\"\\n{'='*50}\")\n    print(f\"📊 {title}\")\n    print(f\"{'='*50}\")\n    print(f\"🎱 前区号码: {' '.join(f'{b:02d}' for b in front_balls)}\")\n    print(f\"🔵 后区号码: {' '.join(f'{b:02d}' for b in back_balls)}\")\n    print(f\"{'='*50}\")\n\ndef main():\n    parser = argparse.ArgumentParser(description='大乐透预测模型')\n    parser.add_argument('--strategy', '-s', type=str, \n                       choices=['hot', 'cold', 'missing', 'balanced', 'ml', 'all'],\n                       default='all', help='预测策略')\n    parser.add_argument('--count', '-c', type=int, default=3, help='生成几组号码')\n    parser.add_argument('--history', type=int, default=None, help='使用最近多少期数据')\n    args = parser.parse_args()\n    \n    records = get_all_records(args.history)\n    \n    if not records:\n        print(\"❌ 数据库中没有数据，请先运行 fetch_history.py 抓取数据\")\n        return\n    \n    print(f\"\\n🎲 大乐透预测模型\")\n    print(f\"📈 数据来源: 最近 {len(records)} 期历史数据\")\n    \n    # 生成后区号码（固定策略）\n    back_balls_pool = list(range(1, 13))\n    \n    if args.strategy == 'all':\n        # 生成多种策略的预测\n        strategies = [\n            ('🔥 热号策略 (高频号码)', 'hot'),\n            ('❄️ 冷号策略 (低频号码)', 'cold'),\n            ('📈 遗漏策略 (长未出现)', 'missing'),\n            ('⚖️ 均衡策略 (冷热混合)', 'balanced'),\n            ('🤖 ML加权策略 (频率+遗漏)', 'ml'),\n        ]\n        \n        for name, strategy in strategies:\n            for i in range(args.count):\n                if strategy == 'hot':\n                    front = generate_hot_number_prediction(records, 5)\n                elif strategy == 'cold':\n                    front = generate_cold_number_prediction(records, 5)\n                elif strategy == 'missing':\n                    front = generate_missing_prediction(records, 5)\n                elif strategy == 'balanced':\n                    front = generate_balanced_prediction(records)\n                else:\n                    front = generate_ml_style_prediction(records)\n                \n                back = sorted(random.sample(back_balls_pool, 2))\n                title = f\"{name} 第{i+1}组\"\n                print_prediction(title, front, back)\n    else:\n        # 生成指定策略的预测\n        for i in range(args.count):\n            if args.strategy == 'hot':\n                front = generate_hot_number_prediction(records, 5)\n            elif args.strategy == 'cold':\n                front = generate_cold_number_prediction(records, 5)\n            elif args.strategy == 'missing':\n                front = generate_missing_prediction(records, 5)\n            elif args.strategy == 'balanced':\n                front = generate_balanced_prediction(records)\n            else:\n                front = generate_ml_style_prediction(records)\n            \n            back = sorted(random.sample(back_balls_pool, 2))\n            title = f\"预测 第{i+1}组\"\n            print_prediction(title, front, back)\n    \n    # 打印统计信息\n    print(f\"\\n📊 历史数据统计 (前区)\")\n    front_freq = analyze_front_balls(records)\n    print(f\"   最热号码: {front_freq.most_common(3)}\")\n    print(f\"   最冷号码: {front_freq.most_common()[-3:]}\")\n\nif __name__ == '__main__':\n    main()\n","path":"/workspace/projects/workspace/skills/super-lotto/scripts/predict.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":404,"output":2418,"cacheRead":49723,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":52545,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778129201714,"responseId":"064b4c32c12b71c5174f01db8c4ad317"},{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"callfunctionj7aeypow1b511","toolName":"write","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully wrote 7922 bytes to /workspace/projects/workspace/skills/super-lotto/scripts/predict.py"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1778129237314},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"预测脚本已创建。现在让我运行它来测试一下效果，并更新 SKILL.md 添加预测功能说明。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"现在测试预测模型：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"callfunctione5kvhnf0ns0j1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /workspace/projects/workspace/skills/super-lotto && python scripts/predict.py --count 2"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":72,"output":99,"cacheRead":52411,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":52582,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total"