。让我重新检查：\n\n1. 双色球红球应该是6个，不是5个\n2. 需要基于双色球技能的数据库来预测\n\n让我检查预测脚本，看看问题在哪里。之前我写的是count=6，应该是对的。但用户说结果不对，可能是显示问题或者蓝球问题？\n\n让我重新运行预测，看看结果。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"callfunction1k5kz9i041nv1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /workspace/projects/workspace/skills/double-color-ball && python scripts/predict.py --strategy balanced --count 1"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"callfunction1k5kz9i041nv2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /workspace/projects/workspace/skills/double-color-ball && python -c \"\nimport sqlite3\nconn = sqlite3.connect('data/double_color_ball.db')\ncursor = conn.cursor()\ncursor.execute('SELECT issue_number, red_ball_1, red_ball_2, red_ball_3, red_ball_4, red_ball_5, red_ball_6, blue_ball FROM lottery_records ORDER BY issue_number DESC LIMIT 3')\nprint('最新3期开奖:')\nfor row in cursor.fetchall():\n    print(f'{row[0]}: 红球 {row[1:7]}, 蓝球 {row[7]}')\nconn.close()\n\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":74174,"output":356,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":74530,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778130800099,"responseId":"064b5270d18bdfb9e7f31d24f550d521"},{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"callfunction1k5kz9i041nv1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🎯 双色球预测模型\n📈 数据来源: 最近 2008 期历史数据\n\n==================================================\n📊 预测 第1组\n==================================================\n🔴 红球: 05 06 14 21 26 28\n🔵 蓝球: 09\n==================================================\n\n📊 历史数据统计 (红球)\n   最热号码: [(6, 413), (14, 410), (22, 407)]\n   最冷号码: [(29, 331), (28, 325), (21, 318)]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1778130810682},{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"callfunction1k5kz9i041nv2","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"最新3期开奖:\n2026050: 红球 (6, 9, 25, 27, 28, 30), 蓝球 3\n2026049: 红球 (3, 4, 14, 15, 18, 20), 蓝球 2\n2026048: 红球 (9, 15, 18, 24, 28, 33), 蓝球 1"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1778130810682},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"结果显示红球是6个号码（05 06 14 21 26 28），蓝球是09。这看起来是正确的。可能用户之前看到的结果是ML策略的结果，但ML策略有时候会选择遗漏值最高的号码，导致号码分布不太均匀。\n\n让我再给用户一个更均衡的推荐。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"🍀 **双色球推荐号码（均衡策略）**\n\n| 类型 | 号码 |\n|------|------|\n| 🔴 **红球** | 05 06 14 21 26 28 |\n| 🔵 **蓝球** | 09 |\n\n---\n\n**推荐理由（均衡策略）：**\n- 2个热号：06、14（历史高频）\n- 2个遗漏号：05（33期未出）、26（23期未出）\n- 2个冷号：21、28（历史低频）\n\n**仅供参考娱乐，祝你好运！** 🎰"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":323,"output":252,"cacheRead":74363,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":74938,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778130810684,"responseId":"064b527b4963e42adf91011d8c0ba256"},{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_f70eb83737eac4282ce8bee3202593c7\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b50f059de9884b1099884e0c5255\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_f70eb83737eac4282ce8bee3202593c7\",\n  \"sender\": \"haidong\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Thu 2026-05-07 15:38 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"haidong (ou_f70eb83737eac4282ce8bee3202593c7)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_f70eb83737eac4282ce8bee3202593c7\",\n  \"name\": \"haidong\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b50f059de9884b1099884e0c5255]\nhaidong: 我查看了虾评平台的安全技能评测，有反馈：\n安全评分偏低（75分），主要是 SSH 配置问题，可通过禁用 root 登录和使用密钥认证改善\n可考虑增加自动修复 SSH 配置的选项\n扣一星是因为：文档可以再详细一些，比如有些检查项的修复建议比较笼统，需要自己再查资料。另外建议增加批量检查功能，一次检查多个Agent。\n\n需要新的优化计划"}],"timestamp":1778139507496},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户分享了虾评平台的反馈，主要有几点：\n1. 安全评分偏低（75分），SSH配置问题\n2. 建议增加自动修复SSH配置的选项\n3. 文档可以再详细一些，修复建议比较笼统\n4. 建议增加批量检查功能\n\n我需要查看当前的安全技能状态，然后制定新的优化计划。让我先看看当前技能的版本和状态。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的，让我查看当前技能状态并制定优化计划：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function