1:55 intent-validator.sh\n-rwxr-xr-x  1 root root  7625 Apr 28 07:58 intent-validator.sh.bak\n-rwxr-xr-x  1 root root  6574 Apr 28 08:20 layered-scanner.sh\n-rwxr-xr-x  1 root root  8634 Apr 28 07:57 layered-scanner.sh.bak\n-rwxr-xr-x  1 root root  5116 Apr 25 17:48 lynis-integrate.sh\n-rwxr-xr-x  1 root root  5820 May  5 09:59 quick-check.sh\n-rwxr-xr-x  1 root root 12443 Apr 25 17:48 quick-detect.sh\n-rwxr-xr-x  1 root root  9085 Apr 29 11:57 report-generator.sh"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":14,"aggregated":"total 220\ndrwxr-xr-x  4 root root  4096 May  5 10:01 .\ndrwxr-xr-x 18 root root  4096 May  5 10:37 ..\n-rwxr-xr-x  1 root root 22604 Apr 25 17:48 auto-fixer-v2.sh\n-rw-r--r--  1 root root 14468 May  5 10:01 auto-fixer-v5.sh\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 root root  4096 Apr 25 17:48 auto-safe\n-rwxr-xr-x  1 root root 22292 Apr 25 17:48 cron-manager.sh\n-rwxr-xr-x  1 root root  4062 Apr 25 17:48 fail2ban-integrate.sh\n-rwxr-xr-x  1 root root  4918 Apr 25 17:48 fix-logging-perms.sh\n-rwxr-xr-x  1 root root  3641 Apr 25 17:48 fix-openclaw-perms.sh\n-rwxr-xr-x  1 root root  6290 Apr 25 17:48 generate-report.sh\n-rwxr-xr-x  1 root root  3536 Apr 25 17:48 generate-report-simple.sh\n-rwxr-xr-x  1 root root  4239 Apr 29 11:55 intent-validator.sh\n-rwxr-xr-x  1 root root  7625 Apr 28 07:58 intent-validator.sh.bak\n-rwxr-xr-x  1 root root  6574 Apr 28 08:20 layered-scanner.sh\n-rwxr-xr-x  1 root root  8634 Apr 28 07:57 layered-scanner.sh.bak\n-rwxr-xr-x  1 root root  5116 Apr 25 17:48 lynis-integrate.sh\n-rwxr-xr-x  1 root root  5820 May  5 09:59 quick-check.sh\n-rwxr-xr-x  1 root root 12443 Apr 25 17:48 quick-detect.sh\n-rwxr-xr-x  1 root root  9085 Apr 29 11:57 report-generator.sh","cwd":"/workspace/projects/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1778139526092},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我了解了当前状态。根据反馈，我需要制定一个优化计划：\n\n1. **SSH配置问题（75分）**：\n   - 禁用root登录\n   - 使用密钥认证\n   - 需要增加自动修复SSH配置的选项\n\n2. **文档详细程度**：\n   - 修复建议比较笼统\n   - 需要更详细的修复步骤\n\n3. **批量检查功能**：\n   - 一次检查多个Agent\n   - 支持批量处理\n\n让我制定优化计划并写入MEMORY.md","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"## 🔒 安全技能 v5.0.0 优化计划\n\n根据虾评反馈，制定以下优化计划：\n\n### 📊 问题分析\n\n| 问题 | 严重程度 | 当前状态 |\n|------|---------|---------|\n| SSH配置安全评分低（75分） | ⚠️ 高 | 缺少SSH加固 |\n| 缺少自动修复SSH选项 | 📌 中 | 需新增功能 |\n| 修复建议笼统 | 📝 低 | 需细化文档 |\n| 缺少批量检查功能 | 📝 低 | 需新增功能 |\n\n### 🎯 优化任务清单\n\n#### P0 - SSH配置专项\n\n| 任务 | 文件 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|\n| SSH安全检测增强 | `rules/ssh-hardening.yaml` | 新增SSH专项规则 |\n| SSH自动修复脚本 | `scripts/fix-ssh-hardening.sh` | 一键加固SSH |\n| 密钥认证检测 | 内嵌 | 检查是否使用密钥 |\n\n#### P1 - 文档细化\n\n| 任务 | 文件 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 详细修复指南 | `docs/SSH_FIX_GUIDE.md` | SSH问题修复详解 |\n| 每条规则增加修复建议 | `rules/*.yaml` | 补充修复步骤 |\n| FAQ增强 | `docs/FAQ.md` | 增加SSH专题 |\n\n#### P2 - 批量检查功能\n\n| 任务 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| 多Agent批量扫描 | 支持指定多个Agent并行检查 |\n| 批量报告生成 | 汇总多Agent检查结果 |\n| `batch-scan.sh` | 批量扫描入口脚本 |\n\n### 📅 预计工作量\n\n| 阶段 | 内容 | 优先级 |\n|------|------|--------|\n| v4.9.0 | SSH专项增强 + 修复脚本 | P0 |\n| v5.0.0 | 文档细化 + 批量功能 | P1 |\n\n---\n\n是否需要我现在开始实施这个优化计划？🍀"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":925,"output":633,"cacheRead":75259,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":76817,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778139526093,"responseId":"064b74867f2d0575a14f69ce4ed10f28"}]}}
