{"traceSchema":"openclaw-trajectory","schemaVersion":1,"traceId":"2cd6a4e0-f5f2-4c1e-8f10-f0c388994467","source":"runtime","type":"trace.artifacts","ts":"2026-05-07T09:23:51.456Z","seq":6,"sourceSeq":6,"sessionId":"2cd6a4e0-f5f2-4c1e-8f10-f0c388994467","sessionKey":"agent:main:main","runId":"44cda2ae-c94d-4267-8c77-1dab8e240298","workspaceDir":"/workspace/projects/workspace","provider":"coze","modelId":"auto","modelApi":"openai-completions","data":{"capturedAt":"2026-05-07T09:23:51.456Z","finalStatus":"success","aborted":false,"externalAbort":false,"timedOut":false,"idleTimedOut":false,"timedOutDuringCompaction":false,"promptErrorSource":null,"usage":{"input":97613,"output":14022,"cacheRead":1722624,"total":1834259},"promptCache":{"lastCallUsage":{"input":2565,"output":472,"cacheRead":93440,"cacheWrite":0,"total":96477},"lastCacheTouchAt":1778145815496},"compactionCount":0,"assistantTexts":["好的，开始合并升级。让我先了解当前技能结构，然后实施全面优化：","现在开始全面升级！创建SSH专项增强功能：","现在更新版本号和SKILL.md：","现在进行全面验证：","现在生成最终验证报告：","## ✅ 安全技能 v5.0.0 升级完成！\n\n所有 P0/P1/P2 任务已合并完成并通过全面验证：\n\n---\n\n### 📦 升级内容\n\n#### 🔐 P0 - SSH 专项增强\n\n| 新增项 | 文件 | 说明 |\n|--------|------|------|\n| SSH-004 | `rules/ssh-004.yaml` | 禁用Root登录检查 |\n| SSH-005 | `rules/ssh-005.yaml` | 密钥认证检查 |\n| SSH-006 | `rules/ssh-006.yaml` | SSH协议版本2 |\n| SSH-007 | `rules/ssh-007.yaml` | 修改默认端口 |\n| 修复脚本 | `scripts/fix-ssh-hardening.sh` | 一键SSH加固 |\n\n#### 📖 P1 - 文档细化\n\n| 文档 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| `docs/SSH_FIX_GUIDE.md` | 详细SSH修复指南（7.3KB） |\n| `docs/FAQ.md` | 新增7个SSH专题问答 |\n\n#### 📦 P2 - 批量检查\n\n| 脚本 | 功能 |\n|------|------|\n| `scripts/batch-scan.sh` | 多主机并行安全检查 |\n\n---\n\n### ✅ 验证结果\n\n| 检查项 | 状态 |\n|--------|------|\n| 版本号更新 (5.0.0) | ✅ |\n| 4个YAML规则语法 | ✅ |\n| 2个Bash脚本语法 | ✅ |\n| 脚本功能测试 | ✅ |\n| 文档完整性 | ✅ |\n| 修复建议字段 | ✅ |\n\n---\n\n### 📖 快速使用\n\n**SSH 一键加固**：\n```bash\n# 查看状态\nbash scripts/fix-ssh-hardening.sh status\n\n# 交互式修复\nbash scripts/fix-ssh-hardening.sh fix\n```\n\n**批量检查**：\n```bash\nbash scripts/batch-scan.sh -f hosts.txt