\"label\": \"haidong (ou_f70eb83737eac4282ce8bee3202593c7)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_f70eb83737eac4282ce8bee3202593c7\",\n  \"name\": \"haidong\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b50f23da7811cb3c3dc940d65bda]\nhaidong: 发布到虾评，然后按照虾评返回的版本号更新到GitHub上。","itemLifecycle":{"startedCount":16,"completedCount":16,"activeCount":0},"toolMetas":[{"toolName":"exec","meta":"print text → run zip healthcheck-v5.0.0.zip → list files in healthcheck-v5.0.0.zip (in /workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill), `cd /workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill && echo \"=== 1. 打包ZIP文件 ===\" && zip -r healthcheck-v5.0.0.zip . -x \"…`"},{"toolName":"exec","meta":"print text → fetch https://xiaping.coze.com/api/upload -> run python3 inline script → show output (in /workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill), `cd /workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill && echo \"=== 2. 上传到虾评平台 ===\" && curl -s -X POST \"https://xiaping.coz…`"},{"toolName":"exec","meta":"print text → run sed on SKILL.md → search \"^version:\" in SKILL.md (in /workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill), `cd /workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill && echo \"=== 3. 更新版本号 ===\" && sed -i 's/^version: 5.0.0/version: 4.8…`"},{"toolName":"exec","meta":"print text → stage git changes → create git commit (in /workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill), `cd /workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill && echo \"=== 4. Git提交 ===\" && git add -A && git commit -m \"Release v…`"},{"toolName":"exec","meta":"print text → run git tag → print text (in /workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill), `cd /workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill && echo \"=== 5. 创建GitHub标签 ===\" && git tag -a v4.8.6 -m \"Release v4.…`"},{"toolName":"exec","meta":"print text → push git changes → push git changes → print text (in /workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill), `cd /workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill && echo \"=== 6. 推送到GitHub ===\" && git push origin main && git push o…`"},{"toolName":"exec","me